headline.main: TEMPERANCE.; Semi-Annual Meeting of the New-York State temperance Alliance--More Scenes of Confusion.

docs.lead_paragraph: The semi-annual meeting of the New-York State Temperance Alliance was held yesterday morning, at Hope Chapel. The attendance early in the day was exceedingly thin. The superior attractions at Metropolitan Hall probably enticed away many of the delegates from their first love. In the course of the morning, however, the audience was consid rably enlarged.
